Text: Thanks from me too. Actually, I see a couple of comics in this archive that I don't already have in electronic form (just some VERY delicate old paper comics which I am too scared to touch)
Thanks a lot for these. Haven't read these comics in ages, good nostalgia trip.

Somehow Uncle Scrooge 011 The Great Steamboat Race went missing on my hard drive!
I will include this missing comic for Set 7 soon!
